Description_lang: Upon reaching full energy Broodtwister Ovi'nax charges towards a full canister of Black Blood and begins devouring it. Feasting upon the canisters contents unleashes torrents of $@spellname441612 every $442432t2 sec and inflicts $442437s1 Shadow damage that absorbs the next $442437s2 healing to all players. Upon finishing the canister, Broodtwister Ovi'nax gains $@spellname443273.
